headline: Paychex Introduces HR Analytics Premium Plus Solution with Built-in GenAI Capabilities
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., November 21, 2024--Paychex, Inc., a leading provider of integrated human capital management software solutions for human resources, employee benefits, insurance services, and payroll, announced today a new premium HR Analytics solution that couples real-time data with generative AI Insights capabilities, providing small- and medium-sized businesses with enterprise-level solutions to help drive more strategic and informed decisions.
